PROPER PEOPLE, PROPER PARTIES
Looking for a proper place to host an event or party? We’d love to share our space and can accommodate groups of up to 150. 

We regularly host after-wedding and bachelorette parties, holiday parties, and more!

Contact us below for more information about scheduling your event. Please see our event menu and general info below.
INQUIRE
If you're just looking to join us for brunch, lunch, or dinner outside of a special event please email us at hello@idyllhoundproper.com or call 850-909-9041 and we will accommodate you as best we can.

About
About Idyll Hound Proper
For nearly a decade, Idyll Hounds Brewing Company has been a beloved destination for local beer enthusiasts and newbies alike. Head Brewer Frasier Hansen has devoted himself to crafting consistently delicious beers that highlight unique flavors of quality ingredients. At IHP, we pair our expertly crafted beers with mouthwatering cuisine from renowned Chef Nick Walton, all in a vibrant and welcoming atmosphere.
We believe that great beer is best enjoyed with friends, and our unbeatable menu and fresh-air dining space provide the perfect setting to do just that. Join us at Idyll Hound Proper for an experience that brings together the best of beer, food, and socializing in a truly proper space. Great Food. Better Beer. Proper People.
